                               int startOffset,
                               eu.cqse.check.framework.scanner.ETokenType startType,
                               String... sequence)
        Returns the index of the first occurrence of the given sequence of strings in the given token list, beginning from the given start offset. The given start type is the type of the sequence's first token. If the sequence is not found, #NOT_FOUND is returned.

      • findAllSequences

        public static List<Integer> findAllSequences(List<IToken> tokens,

                                             eu.cqse.check.framework.scanner.ETokenType startType,

        Returns all indices of occurrences of the given sequence of token texts in the given token list, beginning from the given offset. The given start token type is the type of the first token of the sequence. If the sequence is not found, an empty list is returned.
